1 API Challenge

This API to find out when the ISS (International Space Station) will be passing over Hamburg (which is at latitude 53.5511, longitude: 9.9937):
This API returns times to us in the form of Unix time.

library(glue)
library(httr)
library(jsonlite)
resp &lt;- GET("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/TUHHStartupEngineers/dat_sci_ss20/master/03/bike_data.json", query = list(lat =53.5511, lon = 9.9937))
resp

